Reaching the bottom without walking off will let one find "The Prism". Not much is known about the prism other than that touching it will send one to [[Level 387]]. Unlike The Orb however, The Prism does not move, making one having to traverse to where The Prism is currently located.

===Abandoned Stairs===
Abandoned Stairs is the other set of stairs in this level, which like the rest are in a 10x10 grid. When one enters this sector, they will be met with many broken down and rusty set of stairs and platforms, with some platforms or stairs currently breaking off entirely and floating into space. Many rocks and obstacles can be found on stairs. The further up one goes, the more glitchy it gets. There are usually around 30 levels of platforms, however this can vary. The stairs may also switch to slopes, ladders or escalators halfway to the portal. 

None of these stairs have any effects; the stair's positions are fixed and are unable to be moved. No helpful items can be found in this sector, so one will not be able to survive here for a long time. When one reaches the top, one will find a portal, which when entering the portal will transport one to [[Level 330]]. The portal is the main reason why one may come to this sector of the level. The Portal, unlike The Orb or The Prism, covers the entirety of the top level of platforms. 

===Colonies and Outposts===
Due to the nature of this level, no colonies or outposts could be sustained here.

===Entities===

====The Cubes====
The Cubes are entities controlling the stairs movement and the effects the stairs have. The general appearance of the cubes are floating cubes which vary in colour, which is the effect which the cubes inflict on stairs. Trying to interact with the cubes have seen to be useless, as the cubes have never acknowledged one.  

===Entrances and Exits===

====Entrances==== 

*No-clipping in the hut in [[Level 335]];
*No-clipping in a television that shows a image of space.

==== Exits==== 

*Walking off the Platforms/Slopes in "Reverse Stairs" sends one to [[Level 305]];
*Managing to touch The Orb sends one to [[Level 798]];
*Managing to touch The Prism sends one to [[Level 387]];
*Entering The Portal sends one to [[Level 330]].
